Transport="Motorbike"
BikeCost=2000
print ("When purchased my", Transport, "it cost me £", BikeCost)
BikeCost=BikeCost-200
print ("However a year later with 10% depreciation my bike is now only worth £", BikeCost)
BikeCost=BikeCost-200
print ("After two years the value has dropped a further 10% so the value now is £", BikeCost)
BikeCost=BikeCost-200
print ("After three years and a further 10% drop the value now is £", BikeCost)
BikeCost=BikeCost-200
print ("After four years and a further 10% drop the value now is £", BikeCost)
BikeCost=BikeCost-200
print ("After five years and a further 10% drop the value now is £", BikeCost)
BikeCost=BikeCost-200
print ("Six years after purchase the value of my", Transport, "is now under £1000 as its now only  worth just", BikeCost)
